<para
>simon wird das Tastenkürzel abfangen und mit dem Kommando assozieren.</para>
<para
>Due to technical limitations there are several shortcuts on Microsoft Windows that can not be captured by simon (this includes e.g. Ctrl+Alt+Del and Alt+F4). These special shortcuts can be selected from a list below the aforementioned shortcut button.</para>

