<para
>Of course you can also configure these words in your simon configuration: <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para
><guimenuitem
>Commands</guimenuitem
> 
> <guibutton
>Manage plugins</guibutton
> 
> <guimenuitem
>General</guimenuitem
> 
